  "instructions": [
    "preheat the robata grill to 400f.",
    "brush the eggplant with olive oil and season with salt and pepper.",
    "grill the eggplant for 10 minutes per side, or until tender and slightly charred.",
    "in a small bowl, mix together grated ginger, garlic, and red pepper flakes.",
    "brush the eggplant with the ginger-garlic mixture and grill for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "remove the eggplant from the grill and top with crumbled feta cheese.",
    "drizzle with lemon juice and serve immediately."
  ],
